OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FClive Davis, one of the music
OL,7,Findustry's most powerful figures, who
OL,8,Fhelped launch the careers of
OL,9,Fsuperstars including Whitney Houston
OL,10,Fand Alicia Keys, has died aged 94, his
OL,11,Ffamily have said.
OL,13,FThe award-winning producer shaped the
OL,14,Findustry over the course of his nearly
OL,15,Ffive-decade career, signing and
OL,16,Fmentoring several artists across
OL,17,Fgenres, including Bruce Springsteen,
OL,18,FBilly Joel, Janis Joplin and Carlos
OL,19,FSantana.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
