OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Davis was
OL,7,Fhospitalised following an upper
OL,8,Frespiratory issue and was discharged a
OL,9,Ffew days later.
OL,11,FHe was also diagnosed in 2021 with the
OL,12,Fneurological condition Bell's palsy.
OL,14,FHis death, in his Manhattan apartment,
OL,15,Fwas confirmed by his publicist Aliza
OL,16,FRabinoff, who also shared a statement
OL,17,Ffrom his family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
