OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,F"To the world, our father was the
OL,7,Ficonic music legend whose vision,
OL,8,Finstincts, and relentless pursuit of
OL,9,Fexcellence shaped the soundtrack of
OL,10,Fcountless lives," the statement read.
OL,12,F"He discovered, mentored, and
OL,13,Fchampioned the greatest artists in
OL,14,Fmodern music history, leaving an
OL,15,Findelible mark on culture that will
OL,16,Fendure for generations."
