OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FDavis signed Houston when she was a
OL,7,Fteenager and helped build her career
OL,8,Fwith hits including 'I Wanna Dance
OL,9,FWith Somebody', 'How Will I Know', and
OL,10,Fher chart-topping rendition of 'I Will
OL,11,FAlways Love You'. They became close
OL,12,Ffriends.
OL,14,FHouston became one of the top-selling
OL,15,Fartists in pop history. She died in
OL,16,F2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
