OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FThe music executive was portrayed by
OL,7,FThe Devil Wears Prada star Stanley
OL,8,FTucci in the 2022 musical biopic
OL,9,FWhitney Houston: I Wanna Dance With
OL,10,FSomebody.
OL,12,FHe also launched the career of multi-
OL,13,Fplatinum, multiple-Grammy winner
OL,14,FAlicia Keys, and was quick to note
OL,15,Fother talents he signed, including
OL,16,FJoplin and Billy Joel, Blood Sweat &
OL,17,FTears and other "all-timers," as he so
OL,18,Foften put it.
OL,26,@yD@QOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
