OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782209900
OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,F"I signed Patti Smith, the great
OL,7,FRenaissance woman ... I signed Lou
OL,8,FReed ... I signed the Grateful Dead,"
OL,9,Fhe proudly touted in an interview with
OL,10,FThe Associated Press in 1999.
OL,12,FIn his later years, he was directing
OL,13,Fthe careers of everyone from Barry
OL,14,FManilow to "American Idol" winners
OL,15,FCarrie Underwood and Kelly Clarkson.
OL,17,FAnd his exclusive pre-Grammys gala,
OL,18,Fheld the Saturday night before the
OL,19,FSunday award show every year since
OL,20,F1975, continued to be an institution.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]vD@LOUvD@ZO]
