OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Clive's talent has always been seeing
OL,12,Fand hearing what other people don't,"
OL,13,Fformer President Barack Obama said in
OL,14,Fa video message played at this year's
OL,15,Fgala.
