OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FHe is survived by his four children,
OL,7,Fsons Fred, Doug and Mitchell, daughter
OL,8,FLauren, and his eight grandchildren,
OL,9,FAustin, Charlie, Matthew, Hayley,
OL,10,FHarper, Sloane, Billie and Cody, two
OL,11,Fgreat grandchildren, cousin Jo Schuman
OL,12,Fand partner Greg Schriefer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
