OL,3,CClive Davis, music mogul who launched
OL,4,CWhitney Houston's career dies aged 94
OL,6,FHis family's statement continued: "To
OL,7,Fhis family, Clive was Dad and
OL,8,FGranddaddy, the steady presence at the
OL,9,Fcenter of our lives, the source of
OL,10,Fwisdom, strength, encouragement, and
OL,11,Funconditional love. No matter how
OL,12,Fextraordinary his professional
OL,13,Faccomplishments, he never lost sight
OL,14,Fof what mattered most: the people he
OL,15,Floved.
OL,26,@nD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
